title: $:/config/TiddlyDesktop/AllowRunCommand
tags:

This tiddler enables the `run_command` feature in TiddlyDesktop-RS.

When this plugin is installed and the wiki is loaded in TiddlyDesktop-RS, it will request permission to execute commands. You must approve this request for the `<$action-run-command>` widget to work.

